{"word":"H3960 - לָשַׁן - lâshan - law-shan' - Accuse - குற்றம்சாட்டு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>לָשַׁן"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>lâshan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>law-shan'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Accuse / குற்றம்சாட்டு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அவதூறுபண்ணு, குற்றஞ்சுமத்து"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to use the tongue, to slander"},{"paragraph":"a) (Poel) to slander"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to slander"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) to accuse"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>lick</i>; but used only as a denominative from <a href=\"#/H3956 - לָשֹׁון - lâshôwn - law-shone'/3956\">H3956</a>; to <i>wag the tongue</i>, that is, to <i>calumniate: - </i>accuse, slander."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3956 - לָשֹׁון - lâshôwn - law-shone'/3956\">H3956</a>, <a href=\"#/H3960 - לָשַׁן - lâshan - law-shan'/3960\">H3960</a>, <a href=\"#/H3962 - לֶשַׁע - Leshaʻ - leh'-shah/3962\">H3962</a>"}]}